        <title type="html"><![CDATA[귀납적 사고, 머신러닝]]></title>
        <id>https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/algo/inductive-reasoning-and-machine-learning/</id>
        <link href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/algo/inductive-reasoning-and-machine-learning/"/>
        <updated>2024-08-20T13:33:51.108Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Inductive Reasoning and Machine Learning]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_xtJj" id="귀납적-사고-개념">귀납적 사고 개념<a href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/algo/inductive-reasoning-and-machine-learning/#%EA%B7%80%EB%82%A9%EC%A0%81-%EC%82%AC%EA%B3%A0-%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h2>
<ul>
<li>특정한 사례나 데이터에서 패턴을 발견하고 일반적인 결론이나 규칙을 도출하는 사고방식</li>
<li>데이터 기반 의사결정, 예측 가능성, 지식 확장</li>
</ul>
